{"tid":1641031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無人講！良心capsule！","createTime":"2019-10-09T08:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T05:09:55.000Z","uid":175340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"28783dd439008f40c1b619d6b69ef2bad4f6467a","tid":1641031,"uid":175340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:21:07.000Z","msg":"講真之前都唔知<br />\n原來香港有CAPSULE HOTEL<br />\n直到612見到立場/HK01個d報先留意到<br />\n佢地有份罷工，免費開放俾人休息同沖涼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHrMo7q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHrMo7q.jpg&h=35cea69f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早排見佢地搞眾籌<br />\n話夠數就再免費開放<br />\n表示已經懲罰咗<br />\n但見好似無咩人支持，唔多人捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一波佢地數已找<br />\n依家眾籌緊第二波<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有能力嘅<br />\n一齊幫手大大力懲罰佢</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SLEEEP.hkg/posts/1236261636576535\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSLEEEP.hkg%2Fposts%2F1236261636576535&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=73066c88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SLEEEP.hkg/posts/1236261636576535</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">無能力捐錢嘅<br />\n幫手推俾記者／社工／醫護／無家可歸嘅小朋友<br />\n上去塞爆佢！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw打去問咗<br />\n唔洗證明自己咩職業、咩身份<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔需要出示任何證件</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千祈唔好發開口夢<br />\n靜靜地瞓覺好喇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"